          We make every effort to ensure the accuracy of information presented on this site. However, we cannot guarantee that all information is complete, current, or error-free. Case details and forensic information may be based on publicly available sources that could contain inaccuracies.
        </p>

        <h2>No Glorification of Violence</h2>
        <p>
          Forensic Darkness does not glorify, promote, or encourage violence or criminal behavior. Our content is intended to:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Educate the public about criminal psychology</li>
          <li>Help communities recognize warning signs</li>
          <li>Support crime victims and their families</li>
          <li>Honor the memory of victims</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>
          To the fullest extent permitted by law, Forensic Darkness shall not be liable for any damages arising from the use of this website or reliance on its content.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
